\m \w Yet|strong="H3588"\w* \w my|strong="H5921"\w* lord \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* \w is|strong="H4428"\w* \w like|strong="H3212"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* angel \f + \fr 19:27 \ft Or Angel\f* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* God, \w so|strong="H3588"\w* do \w what|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H4428"\w* good \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w your|strong="H5921"\w* eyes.
