\m 
\v 34 \w But|strong="H4428"\w* \w Barzillai|strong="H1271"\w* replied, “How many years \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w my|strong="H5674"\w* life remain, \w that|strong="H4428"\w* I \w should|strong="H4428"\w* \w go|strong="H5674"\w* \w up|strong="H4428"\w* \w to|strong="H3389"\w* \w Jerusalem|strong="H3389"\w* \w with|strong="H3389"\w* \w the|strong="H5674"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w*?
